# Approach
We Have Use Three Different Approaches :
1. Recursion + Memoization 
    TC : O(n^2) , SC : O(n)
2. Tabulation Method 
    TC : O(n^2) , SC : O(n)
3.  Tabulatuon With SOace Optimised
    TC : O(n^2) , SC : O(1) 


#Note
SC In first two methods is On) and not O(n^2) as size is fixed to 27 for each index hence it is Linear Space ,Similarly for 3rd Method we have optimised to constant space as at any instant we onlt need memory of next 27 blocks  only.

